data.description: Welcome to this absolutely stunning and well-maintained home located in the beautiful gated community, Potranco Run. This home was built in 2014 at just under 2700 square feet and you're less than 25 mins from Lackland AFB, close to shopping, medical, and central to almost anything you need. Key features are 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms, plenty of windows for natural light, an upstairs balcony inside the home, and an outside upstairs balcony patio in the front of the home. You can truly enjoy your spacious downstairs master suite with it's great closet space and luxurious master bathroom with separate tub/shower and double vanity. The secondary bedroom sizes are perfect as well, and all are located upstairs along with a large game room/loft area. The kitchen with separate dining room and breakfast nook rounds out this wonderful, open floor plan. It has a great fenced-in backyard with a covered patio that is ready for your next cookout with friends or family. This home is a must see, so add it to your list and see it before it's gone!
